other_tests.findings: The liver is diffusely echogenic. The contour of the liver is smooth. There is no focal liver mass. The main portal vein is patent with hepatopetal flow. There is no ascites. Bile ducts show no intrahepatic biliary dilation. The CBD measures 11 mm. The gallbladder is borderline distended and contains multiple mobile shadowing gallstones. There is no gallbladder wall thickening or pericholecystic fluid.
